Definition: a shrub of salt marshes of eastern and south central North America and West Indies
Example: fruit is surrounded with white plumelike hairy tufts
Synonyms: groundsel_bush, consumption_weed, cotton-seed_tree, Baccharis_halimifolia, shrub, genus_Baccharis, m, a, of, salt, marshes, eastern, and, south, central, North, America, West, Indies, fruit, is, surrounded, with, white, plumelike, hairy, tufts
Category: noun.plant
